data.description: This charming 2 Bedroom home in Colorado Springs is a nice gem conveniently located near all military bases, schools, and shopping centers. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious open living area with natural light. The kitchen with appliances included, counter space, and a breakfast bar for morning coffee. The Lower Level has 2 Nice Size Bedrooms offering comfortable living space, each with its own closet, full bathroom, and a New Washer and Dryer. The real appeal of this home is its location. Just Minutes away from Fort Carson and all amenities nearby. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your own home. It is the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and cmmunity. Schedule Your Showing today!
